suffix.+ better sanity checking on restored window sizes+ modifier keys checked when item selected, not when menu pulled down+ now using Date: fields for sorting.+ reduced WDS buffers to 61.3b8+ fix click in unhilited scroll bar in mailbox window+ compaction is no longer so memory-piggy+ fixed long recipient bug+ fixed font change bug+ printing now marks as read+ minor mailbox update bug fixed+ cmd-arrow switch now works properly with outgoing mail+ edit menu operational for subject area+ properly setting "dirty" bit when editing subjects+ window activation around hidden progress window fixed+ cursor bug in 1.3a5 fixed+ stingy about disk space+ balloon help with no icon bar bug fixed+ message too large to load now don't cause crashes+ more special characters now detected and disallowed in nicknames+ fixed (some of the) bugs in message retitling+ added "Summaries only" switch to Find window (obscene speeddifference,  if you can use it)+ fixed a bug in big-message skipping code+ ~40% speedup on long finds+ message titling+ fixed windows menu+ mailbox size display moved+ fixed potential difficulty with cancelled dnr lookups+ don't split messages just slightly over the fragment size+ TOC flushing after SMTP+ Show Size also shows mailbox sizes+ added Windows menu+ added BREAK capability (A beta character followed by number of ticks)